Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星外實習作業中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇茜瑪斯喀維校學生一名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然失去聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能滯留在C42廢棄設施中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備完成後第一時間前往救援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿布斯那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己瞎走才遇難的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是自作自受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧氣應該已經用完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全校一霸就此完蛋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆的實習艇真的不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真打算去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想的 亞瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會被連累死的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 有人進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急救措施 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 同學 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.24,0:01:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 等在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昏迷中 但還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 緊急送醫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不等救援隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣說不定…會來不及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時阿布斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧氣罐殘量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎是零了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人可是阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記他怎麼對我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兩碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看著有一線生機的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能見死不救… 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「維甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是移民計劃失敗的受害者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄在火星圈的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新興國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在嚴酷環境下生活的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回那座名為「地球」的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策劃起了規模宏大的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}（歡慶畢業）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 裝飾得好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰幹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一二年級生準備的驚喜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 讓我們典禮結束來活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來就是這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來早了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片打算留在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這張 好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可以留下它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是發你數碼照了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的是貼在這裏的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗是繼續讀書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 本來是這麼打算的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…想重新考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時呆在家裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆要入伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假期結束以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月以後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和學校一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…要加入軍隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 沒告訴過你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面那樣子 比上軍校好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親也這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這麼聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也有考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能幫更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了當兵 還有很多幫助人的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥可不是慈善事業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在是戰爭年代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參戰是保護別人的最佳途徑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆要自立了 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎終於找到了 自己力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己力所能及的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太裝模作樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業典禮要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位親愛的畢業生們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 我想請兩位同學代表大家上台發言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請上台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長又心血來潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 自己一輩子都不會忘記這裏的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想對朋友 想對大家說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 當我們第一天認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個機動戰士癡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我們平時有多遷就你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威！你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你們 每天才這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憲兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以洩漏機密罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即間諜罪 拘捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有拒絕的權力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽見嗎 間諜嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此 可能這傢伙自己就是「維甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特不是的 他是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學 老實一點會對你有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前 你剛轉學來到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘就開始襲擊托爾迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且從那以後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時常出現可疑的電波通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次攻擊前後 通訊頻率增加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要辯解就先去基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間吻合 只因為這種理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就懷疑傑哈特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審查任何一個有嫌疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是維甘…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們… 在一起好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來妨礙調查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想嘗嘗蹲牢房的滋味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說傑哈特騙我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他才是維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放他跑 追！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 受傷沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 你從不會懷疑人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:13:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去衛生室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意 保持隊列
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地毯式排查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 逃進這麼棘手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各小隊 準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 一隻螞蟻也別放跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達斯 多虧你引起騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到撤的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經吩咐Dorado隊待命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始執行佔領托爾迪亞的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許停留得太久了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZedasR 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前確認4台維甘機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台來自衛星外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台似乎潛伏在衛星內的丘陵地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上任不久就有一展身手的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘考慮得真是周到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本隊前往迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 外星佬面前我看誰敢裝孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 剛才逃走的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星守軍難堪重任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 你也出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經裝車往你那裏運了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到學校門前的大路上等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏 或許有過我渴求的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有 忘記故鄉的慘狀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種虛偽的安寧 不是戰士需要的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘給我 滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還留在這座衛星裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛的人是 亞瑟姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的行動…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全…全部被看穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZedasR 果然無法跟上我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對高達 不能將就啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是那種自願走上戰場的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傑哈特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會 在那東西上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是… 維甘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們生在不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙了…我們嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是和你的話 也許能一直做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我作為戰士肩負著責任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有無法讓步的 為之而戰的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有嗎 這樣的覺悟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道是我 你能下手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種善良的傢伙 不適合戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種善良的傢伙 不適合戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入聯邦軍的亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎來作為軍人的初陣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.07,0:24:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的高達嶄露崢嶸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆的啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G Bouncer是沃爾夫隊長的專用機
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.27,0:24:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承了隊長只乘白色機動戰士的傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雪白的機身 太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.69,0:24:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性能方面 因為出自麥德納工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不在高達之下

